<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-05-21T17:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-05-21T17:00:00-05:00" n="515" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d515">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source">811.24591/6a: Telegram</note>
                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to
                                the Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to"><hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi></persName>)</head>
                        <opener>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">
                                <placeName>
                                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-05-21T18:00:00-04:00">May 21,
                                    1943—6 p.m.</date>
                            </dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>250. Iranian Minister here has been instructed to take up with Department
                            question of relations between American military authorities in southern
                            Iran and local Iranian officials. As we understand it, Iranian
                            Government complains that American officers give orders direct to
                            Iranian officials instead of taking up matters through proper
                            channels.</p>
                        <p>Minister states this question has been discussed with you by Iranian
                            Foreign Office.</p>
                        <p>Please let us have any information you have and report steps you may have
                            taken to resolve the difficulty.</p>
                        <closer>
                            <signed>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                            </signed>
                        </closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>